	 <zoopedia_showplatform>
	  <entry>Show Platform</entry>
	 <text>
		<cell pady="0" width="1000"/>
		<p/>
		<cell width="260"/>
		<cell width="640" height="320" bgimg="ui/zoopedia/topCellBg.dds">
		 <cell width="600" padx="20" pady="20">
		  <color r="255" g="255" b="255">
			<img src="entities/objects/buildings/Platform_Show_mm/Platform_Show_mm_icon.dds" sx="0" sy="0" sw="64" sh="64"/>
			<p/>The MC, or master of ceremonies, hosts marine shows from the show platform. Animals, like the California sea lion, perform their tricks on it. Place a show platform in a tank to create a show, and then, click the show platform to open the Show Scheduler.
			<p/>Complete two marine show challenges in Challenge mode to unlock the big-screen TV for your show platform. Complete the Marine Shows campaign to unlock the colorful upgraded show platform with canopy.
		  </color>
		 </cell>
		</cell>
	  </text>  
	 </zoopedia_showplatform>

